{{short description|Military rank of the Rohirrim}}
'''Marshal of the [[West-mark]]''' was a military rank of the [[Rohirrim]], signifying the commander of the armies of western [[Rohan]]. The title was created by the new King [[Éomer]] after the [[War of the Ring]]. The first Rider to hold the rank was King Eomer's lieutenant, [[Erkenbrand]].<ref>{{UT|11b}}</ref>
